sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (uvicorn SSL)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / MySQL<br/>5432/TCP or 3306/TCP
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP or 9000/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: External Client → MLflow API via Gateway

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS /mlflow/api/*<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Platform Auth (gateway-level)
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTPS /mlflow/api/*<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)<br/>Forwarded Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorization Decision
    MLflow->>DB: Query experiment/model data<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL protocol<br/>TLS (optional, via CA bundle)<br/>Connection string credentials
    DB-->>MLflow: Result set
    MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: MLflow Artifact Upload via Serve-Artifacts

    Client->>Gateway: PUT /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/upload-artifact<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Kubernetes Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object (AWS S3 protocol)<br/>TLS (via CA bundle)<br/>AWS IAM credentials (envFrom Secret)
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload confirmation
    MLflow-->>Gateway: Success response
    Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(OpenShift Monitoring)
    Prom->>MLflow: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-ca cert, verified via<br/>openshift-service-ca.crt)<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    MLflow-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
